00:09:38.720 --> 00:09:39.800
Manténgalo.

00:09:40.080 --> 00:09:41.519
Tengo mucho más.

00:09:41.680 --> 00:09:42.359
En caso afirmativo,

00:09:43.800 --> 00:09:44.560
