00:17:28.400 --> 00:17:29.519
¿Es algo urgente?

00:17:32.039 --> 00:17:33.880
Jinghong, tome asiento.

00:17:52.479 --> 00:17:53.200
Jinghong.

00:17:54.559 --> 00:17:57.600
Estás cerca de la Sra. Mu, ¿no?

00:17:59.759 --> 00:18:00.559
Sí.

